  "description": "<p><strong>根据发表在PNAS上的研究报告，频率高于人类听觉的声波可以悬浮微小粒子和液滴，甚至可以移动这些物体。这项发现从材料处理到生物化学等领域都有大量潜在应用。</strong>研究人员已发展出了多种悬浮技术，这些悬浮方法通常是利用静电、磁或者光学原理产生抵消引力所需的力，但它们具有局限性，只适用于特定的金属或磁性材料，对液滴没有任何作用。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eb76b2a/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244871.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%A8%E5%A3%B0%E6%B3%A2%E6%82%AC%E6%B5%AE%E5%92%8C%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244871.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%A8%E5%A3%B0%E6%B3%A2%E6%82%AC%E6%B5%AE%E5%92%8C%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244871.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%A8%E5%A3%B0%E6%B3%A2%E6%82%AC%E6%B5%AE%E5%92%8C%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244871.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%A8%E5%A3%B0%E6%B3%A2%E6%82%AC%E6%B5%AE%E5%92%8C%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244871.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5